  "id": "Hackney-2024_0605",
  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-ec77a302-7fff-0ee7-f574-5b505745af5e&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;The proposal by virtue of its height, massing and close proximity is considered to be harmful to the outlook of residents at the Maisonette 14 Holywell Row and would result in a harmful sense of enclosure and harmful loss of natural light. It therefore fails to comply with Local Plan Policy LP2. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-d5fb059a-7fff-bf30-80ee-5452c6607c45&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposal has not demonstrated that the  development would not increase the risk of flooding on and offsite. Accordingly the proposal fails to comply with London Plan SI13 and its drainage hierarchy, and the Local Plan Policy LP53.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposal fails to demonstrate that it efficiently deals with embodied carbon and therefore fails to comply with the first stage of the energy hierarchy ‘be lean’, whilst the submitted Circular Economy Statement does not adequately justify why many of the existing structural materials cannot be retained. Accordingly, the proposal fails to comply with London Plan Policy SI2 and SI7 and Local Plan Policy LP55.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-18a0f7e9-7fff-e7c2-764e-79e05cb1e545&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-820da64a-7fff-610e-447b-bb19011f502c&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;The proposal, by&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; virtue of its height, scale and massing would appear incongruous and overly dominant within the immediate neighbourhood, harming the character and appearance of the surrounding conservation area, in particular the properties at Holywell Row and visually overwhelming the historic frontages of 64 and 66 Clifton Street. Accordingly, the proposal fails to preserve or enhance the character or appearance of designated heritage assets and is contrary to London Plan Policy HC1 and Local Plan Policy LP3, and by failing to respond to the local character and context, or be compatible with the existing townscape, it is contrary to London Plan Policy D3, D5 and D8 and Local Plan Policy LP1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;"
  ],
